{"tid":303572,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"瞞著老公拍A片 白石茉莉奈8年婚玩完","createTime":"2017-06-30T09:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T00:51:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57fe803495916b0e9fbcaeb1eda05771fef67191","tid":303572,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/174007_30b08a78e37d5210c17feb1173bf4184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F174007_30b08a78e37d5210c17feb1173bf4184.jpg&h=92c7ceb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者陳立妍／綜合報導〕30歲的日本人氣AV女優白石茉莉奈驚傳離婚！2013年出道的茉莉奈，初期靠人妻、人母設定打響知名度，過去她自稱因老公長期在海外工作，難耐寂寞才下海拍AV，離婚消息一出也引發粉絲熱議。<br />\n<br />\n被影迷暱稱為「白石媽媽」的茉莉奈，之前曾透露過育有6歲兒子，因為老公從不看A片，所以也不知道她拍攝A片。AV達人「一劍浣春秋」昨在部落格發文，爆料茉莉奈之前就常以「時間無法配合」或「兒子要放暑假」等理由婉拒邀約，但卻從未提起過丈夫，而在她最新的作品中，則是直接宣布結婚8年的她已經離婚了，但究竟是「真離婚」還是從頭到尾就沒這個人，外界依舊不得而知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2116926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2116926&d=pfJr2N3EbyKllZWmyWlzgE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7e4562b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2116926&h=f308c886\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2116926</a>"},{"pid":"32073bbb43a422f359c36185c58c08bf53a9df07","tid":303572,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"佢真係好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be66d42b792387d7c96db25798376b93bedbcd6","tid":303572,"uid":19979,"like":178,"dislike":2,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"